---
description: Boto3 specific rules
globs: **/*.py
alwaysApply: false
---

- Keep Functions Small and Focused
- Cache or reuse boto3 sessions with lru_cache
- Use botocore’s retry configuration with botocore.config.Config. Avoid custom retry logic.
- Use paginators for listing large sets of resources
- Use waiters to handle resource state changes instead of polling
- Use resource interfaces for higher-level abstractions when available
- Handle AWS service exceptions with botocore.exceptions